1
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:08,080
Do you think this is really going to end?

2
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:11,680
Yes.

3
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,600
It's all over.

4
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,640
It's me, Captain Zhuang.

5
00:02:54,920 --> 00:02:56,650
You guessed absolutely right.

6
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:58,480
Great.

7
00:02:58,960 --> 00:03:01,640
Go to Ping'an Village right now and gather updates on Lu Chen.

8
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:03,160
Cheng Mo and I will meet up with you.

9
00:03:03,160 --> 00:03:03,760
Okay.

10
00:03:09,560 --> 00:03:10,160
Follow me.

11
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:10,960
Where to?

12
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:12,160
We guessed right.

13
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:13,600
Lu Chen slipped up.

14
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,320
Hurry up. Let's go.

15
00:03:20,320 --> 00:03:21,160
Let's go.

16
00:03:30,640 --> 00:03:32,120
Hello, Xiaobai. What's wrong?

17
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:34,160
Hello, Sis. You were right.

18
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,560
There really is such a person.

19
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:36,560
His name is Dong Shan.

20
00:03:36,560 --> 00:03:38,280
He's a security guard at Xinmai Hotel.

21
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:40,240
Lu Chen just left the Investigation Bureau.

22
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,600
Dong Shan also resigned today.

23
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:42,480
He is very likely

24
00:03:42,480 --> 00:03:44,960
the one who helped the killer leave the crime scene.

25
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,280
I've sent you the files.

26
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:46,940
Take a look.

27
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:47,800
Okay.

28
00:03:47,800 --> 00:03:48,480
I got it.

29
00:03:48,480 --> 00:03:50,210
Thanks for your hard work, Bai.

30
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,280
Auntie.

31
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,480
Can you tell me more about Lu?

32
00:04:02,440 --> 00:04:03,320
I want to know more.

33
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:05,040
Asking about Lu,

34
00:04:05,600 --> 00:04:06,720
do you fancy her?

35
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,640
If it were in the past,

36
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:12,040
I would support you.

37
00:04:15,880 --> 00:04:17,000
This poor girl

38
00:04:17,000 --> 00:04:18,079
has had a hard life.

39
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:20,279
Her previous man...

40
00:04:21,680 --> 00:04:22,520
was terrible.

41
00:04:23,560 --> 00:04:24,760
Exactly.

42
00:04:24,960 --> 00:04:27,200
That guy Li was no good.

43
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,280
He used to beat Lu often.

44
00:04:30,680 --> 00:04:33,520
Lu was such a beautiful girl when she married him.

45
00:04:33,520 --> 00:04:34,680
Now look at her,

46
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,760
she looks so pale.

47
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,720
He beat her often,

48
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:39,880
locked her indoors,

49
00:04:39,880 --> 00:04:42,480
and didn't even let her leave the house. What a sin.

50
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:43,159
Oh.

51
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:45,560
Right.

52
00:04:46,080 --> 00:04:48,280
Once, I saw her arms

53
00:04:48,280 --> 00:04:50,200
covered in bruises.

54
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:52,880
When I asked her, she just kept her head down and said

55
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:54,409
she bumped into something.

56
00:04:58,080 --> 00:04:59,720
Things are different lately.

57
00:04:59,720 --> 00:05:01,560
She got a caring man,

58
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,000
and looks much better.

59
00:05:03,040 --> 00:05:04,440
I've seen him a few times.

60
00:05:04,520 --> 00:05:06,360
He's tall

61
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,160
and seems reliable.

62
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,080
Yes.

63
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:10,920
He brings bags of things every time he comes.

64
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,520
Lu's hard days

65
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,360
are finally over.

66
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:20,090
How did you deduce that she had an accomplice?

67
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,840
Because I deduced that

68
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,840
if she wanted to escape quickly,

69
00:05:23,880 --> 00:05:25,280
she couldn't do it alone.

70
00:05:25,760 --> 00:05:29,240
The hotel's dumbwaiter leads to the first-floor staff break room,

71
00:05:29,240 --> 00:05:32,300
but the layout there is different from the guest rooms.

72
00:05:32,480 --> 00:05:35,040
There's a heavy cabinet right outside the dumbwaiter.

73
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:36,080
She needed someone on the outside to help her

74
00:05:36,080 --> 00:05:37,520
so she could get out.

75
00:05:37,520 --> 00:05:38,520
Besides,

76
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:39,960
it only took Lu Chen an hour

77
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:43,400
to appear on the cameras near the village from Mancheng.

78
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:45,920
I think someone must have driven her.

79
00:05:46,159 --> 00:05:47,360
That's my deduction.

80
00:05:50,040 --> 00:05:52,480
Dong Shan is highly likely to be with Lu Chen.

81
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:54,800
We should try to use Lu Chen as a breakthrough.

82
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,400
The chief only gave us three days.

83
00:05:56,400 --> 00:05:58,200
We don't have many chances left.

84
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:03,920
Captain Zhuang.

85
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:06,760
I learned that Lu Chen has long suffered domestic violence from Li Ting.

86
00:06:06,760 --> 00:06:07,720
According to the villagers,

87
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:10,640
another man has appeared around Lu Chen recently.

88
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:12,000
That man is Dong Shan.

89
00:06:12,000 --> 00:06:14,000
Now we even have a motive.

90
00:06:14,960 --> 00:06:16,120
Where is Lu Chen's house?

91
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:16,880
Just walk ahead.

92
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:17,480
Let's go.

93
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:20,520
Is Lu Chen home?

94
00:06:21,160 --> 00:06:21,880
Lu Chen!

95
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,520
Is Lu Chen home?

96
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:26,520
Lu Chen!

97
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,480
Officer Fang.

98
00:06:30,200 --> 00:06:32,060
Officer Zhuang. Why are you here?

99
00:06:32,159 --> 00:06:35,040
There are some procedures that need your signature.

100
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,920
Isn't this case closed?

101
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:39,680
Come in and have a seat.

102
00:06:40,800 --> 00:06:42,080
It's the required procedure.

103
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,280
Please cooperate.

104
00:06:49,640 --> 00:06:50,640
Miss Lu Chen,

105
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:52,159
if you have no questions after reading it,

106
00:06:52,159 --> 00:06:54,000
just sign here.

107
00:07:06,080 --> 00:07:07,720
Look at this photo.

108
00:07:07,720 --> 00:07:10,160
Miss Lu Chen used to be very thin.

109
00:07:13,000 --> 00:07:14,560
I used to be very thin.

110
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,560
I've been sick recently.

111
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:19,220
The medicine I take contains hormones, which made me gain weight.

112
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,200
I've already signed it.

113
00:07:25,200 --> 00:07:26,520
If there's nothing else,

114
00:07:26,520 --> 00:07:28,000
I'd like to rest now.

115
00:07:32,720 --> 00:07:33,920
His name is Dong Shan.

116
00:07:34,280 --> 00:07:36,409
He's a security guard at Xinmai Hotel.

117
00:07:39,400 --> 00:07:40,200
Right?

118
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,720
Are you talking to me?

119
00:07:43,400 --> 00:07:44,920
He was your accomplice.

120
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,680
You killed

121
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,480
Li Ting.

122
00:07:49,080 --> 00:07:50,400
You mean to say

123
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:52,080
I killed Li Ting in Mancheng

124
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:54,760
out of thin air from right here?

125
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:55,600
I'm sorry,

126
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:57,740
but I've never even been to Mancheng.

127
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,640
Miss Lu.

128
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,360
If he's wrong,

129
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,890
you can totally file a complaint against him.

130
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:09,600
But please let him finish speaking, okay?

131
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,200
You did go.

132
00:08:17,320 --> 00:08:19,400
And you went back in Li Ting's car.

133
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:23,000
Zhao Lu mentioned in her statement that

134
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:24,930
when Li Ting returned to the hotel,

135
00:08:25,400 --> 00:08:27,120
he struggled greatly

136
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:29,240
with that suitcase.

137
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:33,280
I watched the surveillance footage repeatedly.

138
00:08:33,280 --> 00:08:37,679
The suitcase Li Ting was carrying looked to weigh about 70 to 80 pounds.

139
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:39,320
But after he died,

140
00:08:39,600 --> 00:08:41,320
when we examined the scene,

141
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:43,440
we didn't find any such heavy object.

142
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:46,080
And I checked that suitcase.

143
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,720
There weren't many

144
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,650
clothes inside.

145
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:52,960
He shouldn't have been struggling so much to move it.

146
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,760
And that extra space

147
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,720
was just enough to fit a person.

148
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,400
So,

149
00:08:58,680 --> 00:09:01,240
she came to the room in the suitcase.

150
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:04,600
But the surveillance footage showed no one left the room.

151
00:09:05,440 --> 00:09:07,240
Then how did she leave?

152
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,840
It must be

153
00:09:13,840 --> 00:09:16,240
the dumbwaiter we kept ruling out.

154
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,280
The dumbwaiter?

155
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,440
Impossible.

156
00:09:19,040 --> 00:09:20,720
The capacity is only 35 kilograms.

157
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,240
Can a person fit in it?

158
00:09:22,920 --> 00:09:24,850
As long as it's under 35 kilograms,

159
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:25,840
they can.

160
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,600
She

161
00:09:28,400 --> 00:09:31,200
doesn't look like she's under 35 kilograms at all.

162
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:32,480
Now,

163
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,490
of course it's impossible.

164
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:36,560
But half a month ago,

165
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:38,000
were you like this?

166
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,050
What did you say?

167
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,480
It took her half a month

168
00:09:40,480 --> 00:09:41,760
to become like this.

169
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:45,320
You must be joking. That's impossible.

170
00:09:45,920 --> 00:09:47,250
It is totally possible.

171
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:49,720
The answer is right here.

172
00:09:52,440 --> 00:09:53,560
Let me guess.

173
00:09:53,880 --> 00:09:57,000
How do we connect a seemingly chubby woman

174
00:09:57,560 --> 00:10:00,600
to the killer who disappeared

175
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,200
from the narrow dumbwaiter?

176
00:10:02,560 --> 00:10:05,840
That is the most brilliant part of your plan.

177
00:10:07,480 --> 00:10:08,800
And these things

178
00:10:08,920 --> 00:10:11,450
are the proof that you gained weight rapidly.

179
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,000
The purpose

180
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,080
was to prove

181
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:16,340
that your body couldn't possibly fit into the dumbwaiter.

182
00:10:17,520 --> 00:10:20,160
Unfortunately, in a short time,

183
00:10:20,160 --> 00:10:22,000
although one can gain weight,

184
00:10:22,000 --> 00:10:23,600
your hands betrayed you.

185
00:10:24,680 --> 00:10:26,560
When we were at the investigation bureau,

186
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,800
I saw that your fingers were very slender.

187
00:10:28,800 --> 00:10:30,920
They don't look like the hands of a plump woman at all.

188
00:10:30,920 --> 00:10:33,240
The speed of fat growth on human hands

189
00:10:33,240 --> 00:10:35,500
is nowhere near as obvious as on the body.

190
00:10:35,640 --> 00:10:36,800
So,

191
00:10:37,120 --> 00:10:38,720
where is that friend of yours

192
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,320
now?

193
00:10:46,280 --> 00:10:47,160
Stop pushing her.

194
00:10:47,160 --> 00:10:47,840
I'm right here,

195
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:48,440
Dong Shan.

196
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,040
Don't run!

197
00:11:01,560 --> 00:11:02,600
Catch him!

198
00:11:08,880 --> 00:11:09,680
Stop!

199
00:11:11,880 --> 00:11:12,940
Hurry, catch them!

200
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,200
This way.

201
00:11:35,920 --> 00:11:36,960
Dong.

202
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:39,440
Forget it.

203
00:11:40,200 --> 00:11:41,600
You've helped me enough.

204
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:44,000
Don't keep making mistakes.

205
00:11:45,720 --> 00:11:47,240
If you want to know the truth,

206
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:48,600
let's check inside.

207
00:11:49,640 --> 00:11:50,840
Open that door,

208
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:54,040
and you'll know what Lu has been through.

209
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:56,440
Lead the way.

210
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,280
Right here.

211
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,120
Take a look.
